src:{"type":"field","size":[329,165],"pos":[2,174],"pattern":46,"border":0,"value":{"text":["verbalize my strategy\n8 ways to win: 3 rows + 3 cols + 2 diagonals\n","num  val\n012  323 - center have 4 ways to win\n345  242 - corners have 3 ways\n678  323 - so tend to take the center, then a corner\n\n","what is savleen's strategy?","\n\n","so: typical game is something like \n\n0:4 x take center\n1:2 o take corner\n2:8 x takes corner,blocks right column\n3:0 o must block\n4:1 x must block\n5:7 o must block\n6:3 x takes only move that might win\n"],"font":["","mono","mono","mono",""],"arg":["","","","",""],"pat":[1,40,36,40,1]}}
