src:{"type":"field","size":[329,165],"pos":[2,174],"pattern":46,"border":0,"value":"You CAN do it this \"symbolic\" way, just from studying board patterns:\n\n\"rules based approach\"\n- easy to give higher values to center/corner\n- easy to give higher value to blocking (occupy same row/col as \n  - easy to block a win on next move\n  - easy to say \"place in same row/diagonal\"\n\nThis is not how most computer games work. Chess was done with pure computation. \n"}
